&gt; 	Subject: RE: [junit] cannot run testing with UI TestRunner?
&gt; 	
&gt; 	
&gt; 
&gt; 	Take a look at the security machinations that Java demands the
&gt; classloader undergo on behalf of the virtual machine. 
&gt; 
&gt; 	I would say that if JUnit can&#39;t complete some very fundamental piece
&gt; of its business because the authors made bad design decisions regarding
&gt; the classloader, you&#39;d need to get someone to go back and refactor JUnit.
&gt; 
&gt; 	Perhaps someone should have tested JUnit with some test software
&gt; before rolling it out. 
